          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1676648262119-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roughly chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong>, 1/3 of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> and 1/3 of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1676648279750-x200.jpg",
